  "page": "Vaes Athjikhari",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Essos.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Vaes Athjikhari is located in Essos\"><img alt=\"Vaes Athjikhari is located in Essos\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/300px-Essos.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/450px-Essos.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/600px-Essos.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 38.9%; left: 68.1%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Vaes Athjikhari\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Vaes Athjikhari</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Essos and the location of Vaes Athjikhari\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Vaes Athjikhari</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is a ruined city in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> in the eastern <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_Sarnor\" title=\"Kingdom of Sarnor\">Kingdom of Sarnor</a>, with <a href=\"/index.php/Omber\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Omber\">Omber</a> to the northwest and the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_the_Ifequevron\" title=\"Kingdom of the Ifequevron\">Kingdom of the Ifequevron</a> to the northeast. Vaes Athjikhari is to the northeast of <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Leqse\" title=\"Vaes Leqse\">Vaes Leqse</a>. The ruined city is situated on the northeastern shore of <a href=\"/index.php/Silver_Shore\" title=\"Silver Shore\">a lake</a>, with a river running north to the <a href=\"/index.php/Bay_of_Tusks\" title=\"Bay of Tusks\">Bay of Tusks</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It was originally called <b>Sallosh</b> or <b>Sallosh by the Silver Shore</b>, but it is now known by its <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_language\" title=\"Dothraki language\">Dothraki</a> name, Vaes Athjhikhari, meaning \"City of Sickness\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafvaes_athjikhari_.28sallosh.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafvaes_athjikhari_.28sallosh.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Athjikhari&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Located on the <a href=\"/index.php/Silver_Shore\" title=\"Silver Shore\">Silver Shore</a>, Sallosh was known as the City of Scholars. Its excellent library contained extensive histories of the <a href=\"/index.php/Tall_Men\" title=\"Tall Men\">Tall Men</a>. The city and its library were destroyed by <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a> which followed the <a href=\"/index.php/Doom_of_Valyria\" title=\"Doom of Valyria\">Doom of Valyria</a>, however.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafvaes_athjikhari_.28sallosh.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafvaes_athjikhari_.28sallosh.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Athjikhari&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><b>Vaes Athjhikhari</b> should be the correct spelling according to Dothraki orthography. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://forum.dothraki.org/beginners/map-translations/\">The Tongues of Ice and Fire</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  The Dothraki Sea.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafvaes_athjikhari_.28sallosh.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafvaes_athjikhari_.28sallosh.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafvaes_athjikhari_.28sallosh.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Vaes Athjikhari (Sallosh).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Grasslands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403102121\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.027 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.029 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 848/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12398/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4280/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1810/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2578/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   20.020      1 -total\n 49.20%    9.850      1 Template:Location_map\n 45.61%    9.131      1 Template:Location_map+\n 33.32%    6.670      1 Template:Location_map~\n 32.97%    6.600      4 Template:Ref\n 18.76%    3.755      4 Template:Ref/core\n 14.72%    2.948     22 Template:Location_map_Essos\n 12.64%    2.531      1 Template:References\n  4.53%    0.906      3 Template:Location_map/decdeg\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:14278-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403102121 and revision id 317113\n -->\n",
